title: Bug 4121: JarExporter causes out of Sync
description: Bug 4121: JarExporter causes out of Sync (1GILQD5)
OB: When using the JarExporter function, the exported jar file includes itself, resulting in an out of sync issue.
EB: The exported jar file should not include itself to avoid the out of sync issue.
SR:
To reproduce the issue: 
1. Invoke the JarExporter function to export a jar file. 
2. Inspect the contents of the exported jar file and note that it includes itself.
